Title: No Shooting Time for Foxes
Writer: Peter Schamoni, Günter Seuren (novel), Günter Seuren (screenplay)
Actors: Helmut Förnbacher, Christian Doermer, Andrea Jonasson, Monika Peitsch
Plot: A young man and his friend Viktor are two young men from a middle-class house. For their families and their society they have nothing left but contempt.
